title: Moneyline Monaco - NFL Week 5 Bets: Cowboys-Rams, Burrow vs Lamar, 49ers-Panthers, Dolphins-Jets
itunes:title: Moneyline Monaco - NFL Week 5 Bets: Cowboys-Rams, Burrow vs Lamar, 49ers-Panthers, Dolphins-Jets
description:
Alex Monaco shares his best bets for Week 5 of the NFL season starting with Joe Burrow and the Bengals facing off against Lamar Jackson and the Ravens in an AFC North showdown.  He then turns his attention to Nick Chubb and the Browns taking on Justin Herbert and the Chargers, Zack Wilson and the Jets up against Tyreek Hill and the Dolphins, Matthew Stafford and the Rams vs Cee Dee Lamb, Ezekiel Elliott and the Cowboys, Jimmy Garoppolo, Deebo Samuel and the 49ers look to stay atop the NFC West as they take on Baker Mayfield and the Panthers. #Volume #Herd #Colincowherd
